Ikabheje a Yeshu gubhannjangwile, “Ishijandikwa, ‘Nnaalinje bhakulungwa a Nnungu bhenu.’”
A Yeshu gubhankalipile lioka jula bhalinkuti “Pumula! Nsheshe munduju!” Bhai lioka jula akanngwiyeje mundu jula pai bhandu bhowe bhalilolesheyanga, ni gwanshoshile gwangali kumpoteka wala kashoko.
Ikabheje kwa ligongo lya gwinji gwa bhandu, bhangakombolanga kujinjiya nkati. Bhai gubhakwelilenje kushipagala, gubhapenwilenje nigubhantulwiyenje mundu jwa poloka jula na mashila, mpaka pakati pakati ja bhandunji mmujo ja a Yeshu.
Ikabheje a Yeshu gubhaimanyi ng'aniyo yabhonji, gubhammalanjile jwa poloka nkono jula, “Jinuka, ujime mmujo ja bhandu bhowe.” Mundu jula gwapite jima mmujo.
Pabha bhanangulungwa bhabhonji bhashinkwatendelanga nneyo peyo ashinkulondola bha unami.”
pabha bhanakwapinganga bhandu bhetu, na bhashikutushenjela shinagogi jila.”
A Yeshu nigubhaabhushiyenje, “Bhai bhandu bha lwene lubhelekolu naalandanyanje na nndi? Paakulandananga na shindu shashi?
Ina gwiigwilile mmibha. Mibha ila ikakuleje guitenjele.
Bhandunji gubhaikengenenje kulola gakoposhele. Gubhaajendelenje a Yeshu, gubhammweninji mundu ashoshilwe na maoka jula, atemi pa makongono ga a Yeshu, awete nngubho, ali na lunda lwakwe lwa mmbone, gubhajogopenje.
Bhai gubhajabhulengenenje pitalunguya Ngani ja Mmbone, shijiji na shijiji na lamya bhalwelenji kila mmbali.
A Petili bhali nkubheleketa genego, gulikoposhele liunde nikwaunishilanga, lyene liundelyo pulyaunishilangaga nigubhajogopenje kaje.
Na mundu juna gwabhabhalanjile, “Mmakulungwa shininkagule, ikabheje nneshe oti ngalajile kumui.”
Gubhajangwile, “Mwaapinje Bhakulungwa a Nnungu bhenu, kwa ntima gwenu gowe, na kwa mbumu yenu yowe, na kwa lunda lwenu lowe, na kwa mashili genu gowe. Na kabhili mumpinje nntami nnjenu malinga shinkwiipinga mmayene.”
Nkali anajumushe nikumpa kwa ligongo lyabha mmbwiga mwine, ikabheje, kwa ligongo lya punda juga, shajumushe nikumpa shoshowe shaajuga.
Bhai monaga shiilu shenu showe shikolaga shilangaya gwangali pakwete lubhindu, shene shiilusho shishibhe na shilangaya kwa kaje, malinga kandili shijikuti kummulishila kwa shilangaya shakwe.”
“Jojowe abheleketa malobhe ga nyata kuka Mwana juka Mundu shaleshelelwe, ikabheje akunkupulu Mbumu jwa Ukonjelo akaleshelelwa.
Nkali bhabhuje pakati shilo eu kumashelo, mbaya bhene bhatumishi bhushiaimananje bhalisheyanga!
Bhai, gubhammalanjile ntumishi jwabho, ‘Lola! Kwa yaka itatu natendaga kwiya kabha iepo ya gwene nkongogu, nangapata shoshowe. Guushele! Kwa nndi unaangabhanya litaka gwayoyo?’
Nnolanje! Shinneshelwanje ushubha nshilambo shenunji. Bhai, ngunakummalanjilanga, nkamonanga kabhili mpaka pushimmeleketanje kuti, ‘Bhakwete Mboka bhene bhakwiya kwa lina lya Bhakulungwa.’ ”
Pabha, gani munkumbi gwenunji apingaga kushenga nnala, akatandubha kutama nilola galama jakwe nkupinga amumanye ibhaga akwete mmbiyaya malila?
“Ikabheje ali kwaataliya, ainagwe gubhamweni, nikummonela shiya gubhammutushile kukunnyambatila akuno bhalikunnambanga.
“Shalia na ashinkulondola, yaapali mpaka malanga ga a Yowana Bhabhatisha. Kutandubhila penepo, ngani ja mmbone ja Upalume gwa a Nnungu jinalunguywa, na kila mundu anakwiijinjiya kwa mashili.
Bhalijinjila nshilambo shimo, bhandunji kumi bhamangundula bhashinkwajiilanga a Yeshu, gubhajimingene kwa taliya.
Na nshilambo shosho, bhashinkupagwa bhakongwe bhamo bhashitenga bhatendaga kwaajendela bhene bhaukumula bhala bhalinkuti, ‘Nng'ukumule mbate aki jangu kuka mmagongo nnjangu.’
A Yeshu gubhaatolilenje likumi limo na bhabhili bhala kunyenje, nigubhaabhalanjilenje, “Mpilikananje! Tunajomboka kuloya ku Yelushalemu, kweneko gowe gajandikwe na ashinkulondola gaka Mwana juka Mundu shigatimilile.
Ntumishi jwa ntai gwaishe nigwashite, ‘Mmakulungwa ela imwambele ila, ipatikene pwaida likumi limo.’
Shibhakukandaganye ugwe na ashibhanago nkati pemo. Na bhakalekanga nkali liganga limo lijimi pa liganga lina, pabha gwangagamanya malanga ga ntapulo gwako.”
Bhai, bhatumilwenje bhala gubhaabhushiyenje a Yeshu, “Mmajiganya, tumumanyi mmwe nnabheleketa na kujiganya indu ya uguja na mwangali luagu, mmwe nnajiganya indu ya a Nnungu ipinjikwa bhandu bhatendanje.
Kwa ugulumba, bhanakwaatolelanga bhanabhakongwe bha shitenga indu yabhonji, bhalikwiitembanganga kuti bhanguja, bhalikwaajuganga a Nnungu kwa leupya. Bhene bhanganyabho shibhaukumulwanje kupunda bhananji.”
Malanga gushigatandubhe genego kukoposhela, nnjimangane, nnjinulanje meyo genunji kunani, pabha kugombolwa kwenunji kubhandishile.”
Pabha ngunakummalanjilanga, ngang'wa kabhili divai ja shabhibhu mpaka Upalume gwa a Nnungu pushuishe.”
Gubhaabhushiyenje, “Pakubha nnagonanga? Nnjumukanje maajuganje a Nnungu, nnajinjilanga mmalinjilo.”
Gubhatandubhenje kwaashitakiya bhalinkutinji, “Bhene bhandubha bhatendaga kwaapuganyanga bhandunji bhetu, bhalikwalimbiyanga kulipa koli kwa a Kaishali na bhalikwiishema a Kilishitu na a mpalume.”
Penepo, bhandunji shibhailugululanje itumbi, ‘Ntugwilanje!’ Na ijomboya, ‘Ntuunishilanje’!
Gubhaimenenje liganga lya ibhila palikabhuli pala linokolelwe kunyenje likabhuli.
Bhakatameje kulya nabhonji, gubhatolile nkate, gubhatendile eja kwa a Nnungu, gubhaugebhenye, gubhaapelenje.
Shilangayasho shinalangaya pa lubhindu, wala lubhindu lwangakombola kuima shilangaya.
Nne namwene ngaamanyiji, ikabheje njikwiya bhatisha kwa mashi nkupinga bhandu bha Ishilaeli bhaamanyanje.”
Kungai gubhaalugulilenje bhatumishi, “Nnaino ntekanje nkaapanganje bhakulungwa bha kalamu.”
Kweli ngunakummalanjila, uwe tunabheleketa itukwimanya nikong'ondela ituibhweni, ikabheje mmanganya nkaakundanga ntenga gwetu.
Bhai, a Yeshu bhakagamanyeje genego, gubhajabhwile ku Yudea kubhuja ku Galilaya,
Gene malanga pego bhaajiganywa bhabho gubhaashondelesheyenje a Yeshu bhalinkutinji, “Shonde Mmaajiganya, nnye shalya.”
Bhai, penepo ashinkupagwa nnwele jumo alwalile yaka makumi gatatu na yaka nane.
Mmanganyanji nshikwaatumanga bhantenga kwa a Yowana, na bhalabho gubhakong'ondele ga kweli.
Bhandu bhakashibhonanjeje shene shilangulo shibhatendile a Yeshu, gubhashitenje, “Kweli bhenebha ankulondola bha a Nnungu bhakwiya kushilambolyo.”
Gubhashitenje, “Bhuli, aju nngabha mwana gwabho a Yoshepu? Twaamanyi ainagwe na akwabhe! Bhai abheleketa bhuli kuti ashituluka kopoka kunnungu?”
A Yeshu gubhaalugulilenje, “Bhuli, nanganng'agulanga mmanganya likumi limo na bhabhili? Nkali nneyo, jumo munkumbi gwenunji ni Lishetani!”
Ikabheje tukumanyi abha bhandubha kubhakoposhele, a Kilishitu pushibhaishe jwakwa mundu shakumanye kubhakoposhele!”
Malabhi gakwe lyambape gubhapite kabhili ku likanisha. Bhandu bhowe gubhaajendelenje, nigubhatemi kwaajiganyanga.
Pubhabheleketaga genego, bhandu bhabhagwinji gubhaakulupalilenje.
A Yeshu gubhaalugulilenje, “Kweli ngunakummalanjilanga, nne naapali, a Bhulaimu bhakanabhe pagwa.”
Jwene mundujo gwabhajangwilenje, “Nimmalanjilenje, mmanganyanji mwangapilikanishiyanga, kwa nndi nnapinganga kupilikana kabhili? Bhuli na mmanganyanji nnapinganga kubha bhaajiganywa bhabho?”
Nne nshunga jwa mmbone. Bhalinginji bhangu naamanyinji, na bhalabhonji bhalinginji bhangu bhamanyinji,
Penepo bhandu bhabhagwinji gubhaakulupalilenje a Yeshu.
Bhakamaliyeje kubheleketa genego, a Malata gubhapite kukwaashema a Maliya, apwabho, gubhaabhalanjile kuntemela, “Bhaajiganya bhaishe bhanakunshema.”
Bhai, pubhalinginji nkwaaloleya a Yeshu. Bhakaimananjeje pamo nnikanisha, gubhabhuyenenje, “Nkubhonanga bhuli? Igala bhakaika kushikukuu kuno?”
A Yeshu gubhaajangwilenje, “Malanga ga kuywa Mwana juka Mundu gaishe!
A Yeshu gubhabhelekete kwa lilobhe lya utiya, “Mundu angulupalila nne, akaangulupalila nnepe, ikabhe anakwaakulupalila bhandumile bhala.
Bhaajiganywa gubhalolenenje akuno bhalinginji na lipamba gani jubhakuntaya.
Kweli ngunakummalanjilanga, jwene angulupalila nne, na jwalakwe shaatende maengo gungukamula nne, nkali na gamakulungwa kupunda genega, pabha nne ngunakwenda kwa Atati.
Nne ngunakumpinganga mmanganyanji malinga Atati shibhambinga nne. Ntamangane nkupingana na nne.
Kwa ngani ja yambi yenunji shabhakong'ondelanje, pabha bhangangulupalilanga nne,
Nne njikunkuya mmwe pa shilambolyo pano, maliye liengo limwaambele ndende lila.
Bhai, a Yeshu bhakaalugulilanjeje kuti, “Nne ni nne” gubhanokolenenje kubhuja nnyuma gubhaagwilenje pai.
A Yeshu gubhaajangwile, “Bhuli! Genego malobhe genu mmayene, eu nshibhalanjilwa na bhandunji, gangu nne?”
Bhai Bhayaudi bhabhagwinji gubhashomilenje jene mmbilajo, pabha pubhaabhambilenje munshalabha a Yeshu, pupaaliji tome na shilambo. Na jene mmbilajo pujajandikwe kwa Shiebhulania na Shilatini na Shigiliki.
Bhai a Petili na nkujiganywa juna jula, gubhapitengene kulikabhuli.
Ikabheje yenei ishijandikwa Mmajandiko ga Ukonjelo kuti, nkupinga nkulupalilanje kuti a Yeshu ni a Kilishitu, Mwana jwa a Nnungu, na nkulupalilangaga nkolanje gumi kwa mashili ga lina lyabho.
Kwa mobha makumi nsheshe bhakaweje, bhashinkwilangula papagwinji kubhaajiganywa bhabho. Bhatendaga kwaabhonanga a Yeshu na bhalabho bhatendaga kungulushila ga Ukulungwa gwa a Nnungu.
