Bhashikunng'ukumula lijajana nkulu,
Ashinkuwala lijoo lishubhikwe mminyai. Na jwenejo lina lyakwe, “Lilobhe lya a Nnungu.”
Na bhene bhatemi pa shitengu sha ukulungwa bhala gubhashite, “Nnole, ngunaatenda yowe kubha ya ambi.” Kabhili gubhamalanjile, “Nnjandishe kuti, gene malobhe gano, ni gaakulupalika na ga kweli!”
Numbe jwene malaika jula nigwanugulile, “Gegano malobhe gano ni gaakulupalika kaje na ga kweli. Bhakulungwa a Nnungu bhakwaapanganga a ashinkulondola Mbumu jwabho, bhashinkutuma malaika jwabho, kukwaalanguyanga bhatumishi babho gene gapinga koposhela shangupe gala.”
